from pyquil import Program 

from pyquil.gates import * 

from pyquil.quilbase import Declare

circuit = Program(
Declare("ro", "BIT", 2),
H(0),
CNOT(0, 1),
MEASURE(0, ("ro", 0)),
MEASURE(1, ("ro", 1)),
)
